00:46:35,924 --> 00:46:36,758
Apa?

875
00:46:37,342 --> 00:46:38,676
Dia sudah datang.

876
00:46:39,177 --> 00:46:41,971
Dokter Ahn sudah di Ruang Persalinan
sejak sepuluh menit lalu.

877
00:46:42,764 --> 00:46:43,890
